Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投影魔术就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将心里想的物质 以拟似的样貌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投射到现实中的术式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了把内部的世界 投影到外部的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须正确地理解自己与他人的区别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯尼斯老师 我有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么疑问？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦伯·维尔维特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了正确的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能进行任何投影吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着眼点还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只有着眼点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算理论正确
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种血统的人也无法实践
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说得没错 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新来的人做不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为魔术师不能只看血统
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说过必须有正确的理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦伯·维尔维特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术回路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血统
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是无法改变的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠认知就想颠覆现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本是妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就向您证明血统不代表一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么等你证明成功后再来大放厥词
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空有想法而没有证明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本一文不值
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么肯尼斯老师的时间比黄金宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然随便浪费掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单来说你太格格不入了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新来的人只是时钟塔凑数用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 阿姆雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦伯正用他的方式努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不具备优良血统的努力哪有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为你们认为无法证明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以联合起来恐吓我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就证明给大家看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你根本办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就做给你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别理那个吊车尾的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我现在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,净是一堆严肃的破书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是师父以前的书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须小心地对待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破书怎么照顾还是破破烂烂的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有新信件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斗篷的颜色要更…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 首先调整肌肉量…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微再瘦一点比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 格雷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再玩网络游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才太专注于创造虚拟角色了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是师父吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别一直盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会不太自在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 找我有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是您的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从时钟塔转寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是上个月的日期吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时钟塔何时才要改善信件的效率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同学会啊…
