Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我实在搞不定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马里斯比利老师是真正的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是提出分析的建议而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过谦虚反而会惹人厌喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到天才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那位苍崎橙子回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位人偶师？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像那种老是闯祸的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽路玛那时候 不知道给我添了多少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要提到她？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你跟她有点关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该早已掌握她的动向了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不幸地 光是我自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就忙不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔加玛丽小姐圣诞节 打算怎么过呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是跟往常一样自习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不跟朋友出去玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪有朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不嫌弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要来我们家？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算跟莱妮丝小姐她们看电影过节
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身为下任君主 不用参与这类…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻时代的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候会成为最大的财产
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特丽莎也曾经说过 与他人制造回忆是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我还是去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦伯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是韦伯·维尔维特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡缪·佩利戈尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到能再这跟你们重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡缪 阿姆雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我委托他们工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天会找你来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是因为他们推荐你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟投影是你们两个人的专业嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是让你晋升典位的研究啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最先出人头地的风采
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是被你抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投影是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是像这样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将投影当做使魔来使唤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将其命名为外壳投影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是电脑游戏的角色一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与自己联系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这个分身不是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不仅是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有高度自律性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远比一般的投影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加持久 动作也更精密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到这项技术的重点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为能用这项技术模拟出整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟出…世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为这一定很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚点再打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让朋友失望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 请恕我先行告退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 晚点见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过太令人吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到卡缪和君主是同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我从圣杯战争归来后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她早就离开了时钟塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为你跑去环游世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你也忘了我的长相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我看走眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少还记得名字就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在她以佩里戈尔公司的CEO身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来协助我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩里戈尔是那家电脑公司吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我离开时钟塔之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因缘机会接触到高科技
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆雷斯也对我们投资了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很享受玩佩里戈尔出的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你就是老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 真不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那台相机还跟以前的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这是家父的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直舍不得淘汰它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能像以前一样让我拍张照吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是跟以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是爱拍照的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以请你按快门吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这点小事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以带着兜帽拍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要拍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说照片洗好会寄给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是底片照片才有的醍醐味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道师父有这么棒的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是只认识像梅尔文那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待同学会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.98,Style,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\bord0\fsp28\c&H0000B1&\t(0,950,\blur0)\pos(966,370)}君主•埃尔梅罗二世事件簿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.98,Style,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs63\bord0\fsp14.5\c&H0000B1&\t(0,950,\blur0)\pos(746,660)}魔眼搜集列车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.98,Style,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs63\bord0\fsp9.2\c&H0000B1&\t(0,950,\blur0)\pos(1275,660)}特 别 篇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.98,Style,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs60\bord0\fsp6.2\c&H0000B1&\t(0,950,\blur0)\pos(1044,660)}Grace note
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.98,Style,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs30\bord0\fsp9\c&H0000B1&\t(0,950,\blur0)\pos(786,565)}Rail Zeppelin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都来这里听课了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然给我迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…应该不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于达到根源的境界了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有别的可能了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是游戏的结局 比想象中还长之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 老师好像来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟守卫解释花太多时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事？是红色的糖果吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是黑色组织…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望您能好好地解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早上起来就变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会变成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都不知道 我怎么会知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢？ 路·希安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闻起来确实是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力波形也是老师 没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就没错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾 到底发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上起来就变成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我劝他休息比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他说不能随意暂停授课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个工作狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停课不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我上课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有这号人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得有点可爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点太年轻了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之不调查出原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法好好上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象中还好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这人竟是我那老板着脸的兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很在意好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你可以叫我姐姐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你让我忍不住想欺负你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你糖果好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖果？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是日本大都市 大阪的风俗习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,费拉特这家伙到底教了她什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我中了高级幻术之类的魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会侵蚀他人的认知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的衣服就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起初我的衣服尺寸完全不合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在却被调整成以前的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己和周围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认知都被改写 以为我返老还童
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会没有烟草味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白说现在完全无法接受烟酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我的人格就会消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样有点恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的资料 现在还是维持原状吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 没有动过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要借来看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这种反应 是平常的兄长大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摘取这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印象与认知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果假设这只是虚拟外观
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必要的条件…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是…显象吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找师父有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想找他叙旧 但是老找不到他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么您要进来等吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父应该会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆就一直维持这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真{\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\fs75}啰嗦{\fn\fs}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化野 情况如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你满意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是法政科干的好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气的模样真像个十几岁孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是思考被身体年龄影响而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要继续吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到现在还是不擅长整理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从以前就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 以前就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦伯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡缪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父以前是个怎样的学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不切实际的韦伯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家曾经这么称呼他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼高手低
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时的我确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还记得你的论文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“问鼎新世纪魔导之道”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那篇真的写得很烂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我家也是暴发户
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴你写了那篇论文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师是位真诚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读了我这种人的论文 还提出反论
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他个性很差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候还真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然大家的回忆里应该没有我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直是帮大家拍照的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才没有自己的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道当时自己是怎样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴你还记得我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 格蕾 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦伯是怎样的老师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父他是一个很棒的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我想确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天同学会你会来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这幅模样出席？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是之前的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗？你就这样放她回去吗？你这个懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是这幅德性 才会变成万年单身处…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集费拉特他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不想牵扯到学生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是比闹出人命好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦伯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我十年的光阴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:09.98,Style,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs90\bord0\fsp22\c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,950,\blur0)\pos(966,405)}君主•埃尔梅罗二世事件簿
